# uSv/hr is cumulative over an hour?
# 500 CPM = 0.5 mR/hr milliRad
# 1 rem = 0.01 Sv
# 120 CPM = 1 uSv/hr
# 2 CPS = 1 uSv/hr
# 100 CPM = 1 uSv/hr?
